Eunic - A Bash script to Manage Unicorn

Install:
=======

In the source directory where you downloaded this repo:
cp eunic /usr/local/bin
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/eunic

Command Usage:
==============

Restart:
    eunic -R production

Start:
    eunic -S production

Stop:
    eunic -s production

There is the USR reload thing in here but f'd if I can get USR to work. I should try again.

